//to them and saved them. They were so cool, I used to watch;
//them for hours. This preset is then one that flowed from;
//changing and tweaking those.;
//Almost everything is changed, but the one shape, (shape 4);
//feeding back into the two bigger ones (shape 2 and 3) is;
//obtained from the Feedback presets.;
//I've added a 4th shape (shape 1) that is the big 'filter';
//to change colours etc.  It is also textured, so thats why;
